    "body": "Indeed, it was not clear :)\n\nBy network change, I meant the fact that the user is changing the network. For instance, going from mainnet to testnet or to a custom rpc.\n\nAs far as I know, the current network and the current account are the only 2 contextual information that are relevant. As you mentioned, the rest can be figured out using web3 itself.\n",
